Other Changes in the Sales Cloud

Identify Potentially Risky Contacts on Deals

With a new insight in Pipeline Inspection, sales reps can now learn whether a contact is a detractor on one of their deals. To see the detractor’s relationships with other contacts on the deal, reps can view the Buyer Relationship Map directly from the insight.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Einstein 1 Sales Edition editions with Sales Cloud and with Buyer Relationship Map enabled.

How: The contact detractor insight is shown in the Pipeline Inspection side panel when it’s found for an opportunity that has a Buyer Relationship Map created.
title: Identifying Potentially Risky Contacts in Salesforce
